Package: openairmaps
Type: Package
Title: Package to Plot Openair Outputs and Static and Leaflet Maps
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("David", "Carslaw", role = c("aut", "cre"), email =
    "david.carslaw@york.ac.uk"))
Description: Package to support openair for plotting on various maps. The maps
    include those available via the ggmap package e.g. Google Maps and leaflet maps
    for plotting bivariate polar plots.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
